name: Margherita Pizza
description: Classic Italian pizza topped with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, fresh basil leaves, and a drizzle of olive oil.

name: Sushi Roll Combo
description: Assorted sushi rolls including California roll, spicy tuna roll, and salmon avocado roll. Served with pickled ginger, wasabi, and soy sauce.

name: Chicken Tikka Masala
description: Tender pieces of grilled chicken cooked in a creamy tomato-based sauce with aromatic Indian spices. Served with basmati rice and naan bread.

name: Caesar Salad
description: Crisp romaine lettuce tossed with Caesar dressing, parmesan cheese, croutons, and a sprinkle of black pepper.

name: Beef Burger
description: Juicy beef patty topped with cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomato, onion, pickles, and mayonnaise. Served on a toasted sesame seed bun.

name: Pad Thai Noodles
description: Stir-fried rice noodles with tofu, bean sprouts, peanuts, egg, and a tangy tamarind sauce. Garnished with lime wedges and cilantro.

name: Spaghetti Carbonara
description: Pasta tossed with crispy bacon, eggs, Parmesan cheese, and black pepper, creating a creamy and flavorful sauce.

name: Chicken Shawarma Wrap
description: Grilled marinated chicken wrapped in warm pita bread with lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and tahini sauce.

name: Beef Tacos
description: Soft corn tortillas filled with seasoned ground beef, lettuce, cheese, tomatoes, and salsa.

name: Vegetable Stir-Fry
description: Assorted vegetables such as broccoli, bell peppers, carrots, and snap peas stir-fried in a savory sauce. Served over steamed rice.

name: Caprese Salad
description: Fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and basil leaves drizzled with balsamic glaze and olive oil. A simple and refreshing Italian salad.

name: Beef Pho
description: A fragrant broth with rice noodles, thinly sliced beef, bean sprouts, Thai basil, cilantro, and lime wedges. Served with hoisin sauce and sriracha.

name: Mushroom Risotto
description: Creamy Arborio rice cooked with mushrooms, onions, garlic, white wine, and Parmesan cheese. A comforting and indulgent Italian rice dish.

name: Fish and Chips
description: Crispy battered fish served with thick-cut fries (chips), mushy peas, tartar sauce, and a wedge of lemon. A quintessential British pub dish.

name: Falafel Wrap
description: Crispy chickpea fritters wrapped in warm pita bread with lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and tahini sauce.

name: Lasagna
description: Layers of pasta sheets, marinara sauce, ricotta cheese, mozzarella cheese, and ground beef, baked to perfection. A hearty and comforting Italian classic.

name: Chicken Caesar Wrap
description: Grilled chicken breast, romaine lettuce, Caesar dressing, and Parmesan cheese wrapped in a flour tortilla.

name: Paneer Tikka Masala
description: Chunks of paneer (Indian cottage cheese) marinated in yogurt and spices, cooked in a creamy tomato-based sauce. Served with basmati rice and naan bread.

name: Hawaiian Poke Bowl
description: A bowl of rice topped with fresh diced raw fish (usually tuna or salmon), avocado, cucumber, edamame, and seaweed, dressed with soy sauce, sesame oil, and other seasonings.

name: Tom Yum Soup
description: A hot and sour soup made with lemongrass, galangal, kaffir lime leaves, mushrooms, shrimp, and chili peppers. A signature dish of Thai cuisine.

name: Pulled Pork Sandwich
description: Slow-cooked pulled pork smothered in barbecue sauce, piled high on a soft bun, and topped with coleslaw. A Southern comfort food classic.
